OL,7,FMandelson, who became the MP for
OL,8,FHartlepool in 1992 and helped Tony
OL,9,FBlair's New Labour reach victory, will
OL,10,Fnow become the UK's ambassador to the
OL,11,FUS, as ITV News' Harry Horton and
OL,12,FRobert Moore explain
OL,14,FA campaign adviser to US President-
OL,15,Felect Donald Trump has called Lord
OL,16,FPeter Mandelson an "absolute moron"
OL,17,Fafter the Labour peer was confirmed as
OL,18,Fthe next UK ambassador to the US.
