OL,7,FMandelson said on Friday it was a
OL,8,F"great honour" to serve the country
OL,9,Fand become the top UK diplomat in
OL,10,FWashington at a crucial time for UK-US
OL,11,Frelations as Trump becomes president.
OL,13,FHe will take over from Dame Karen
OL,14,FPierce in the new year, Prime Minister
OL,15,FSir Keir Starmer said.
