OL,7,FChris LaCivita, who served as senior
OL,8,Fadvisor to Trump's 2024 presidential
OL,9,Fcampaign, criticised the British
OL,10,Fgovernment's decision saying it was
OL,11,Freplacing a "professional universally
OL,12,Frespected Ambo (ambassador) with an
OL,13,Fabsolute moron".
OL,15,FIn a post on X, he said Mandelson
OL,16,Fshould "stay home", adding: "Mandelson
OL,17,Fdescribed Trump as a danger to the
OL,18,Fworld and 'little short of a white
OL,19,Fnationalist'."
