OL,8,FTelegraph which reported on Mandelson
OL,9,Fdescribing Trump as a "danger to the
OL,10,Fworld" and "little short of a white
OL,11,Fnationalist and racist".
OL,13,FIt comes after Starmer confirmed that
OL,14,FMandelson, who is co-founder of Global
OL,15,FCounsel, a global public policy
OL,16,Fadvisory firm, would take on the role.
OL,18,FThe prime minister said: "I am
OL,19,Fdelighted to appoint Lord Mandelson to
OL,20,Fbe the next British Ambassador to the
OL,21,FUnited States of America.
