OL,7,F"I would also like to thank Dame Karen
OL,8,FPierce for her invaluable service for
OL,9,Fthe last four years, and in particular
OL,10,Fthe wisdom and steadfast support she
OL,11,Fhas given me personally since July.
OL,12,FShe made history as the first woman to
OL,13,Fserve as U.K. Ambassador to the U.S.
OL,14,Fand she has been an outstanding
OL,15,Frepresentative of our country abroad.
OL,16,FI wish her all the very best in
OL,17,Ffuture."
