OL,7,F"We face challenges in Britain but
OL,8,Falso big opportunities and it will be
OL,9,Fa privilege to work with the
OL,10,Fgovernment to land those
OL,11,Fopportunities, both for our economy
OL,12,Fand our nation's security, and to
OL,13,Fadvance our historic alliance with the
OL,14,FUnited States," he added.
OL,16,FNow 71, Mandelson served as a cabinet
OL,17,Fmember in both Tony Blair's and Gordon
OL,18,FBrown's governments where he was known
OL,19,Fas the "Prince of Darkness" in his
OL,20,Frole as New Labour's spin doctor.
