OL,7,FMandelson has been seen as a divisive
OL,8,Ffigure within Labour having resigned
OL,9,Ftwice from Blair's cabinet, once for
OL,10,Fan undeclared loan and again after
OL,11,Finvolving himself in the application
OL,12,Fof a British passport.
OL,14,FHe became the MP for Hartlepool in
OL,15,F1992 and helped Blair's New Labour
OL,16,Freach victory.
OL,18,FHe served as Trade Secretary and
OL,19,FNorthern Ireland Secretary before
OL,20,Fstepping down to become EU trade
OL,21,Fcommissioner in 2004.
