OL,8,FLabour's appointment of Mandelson
OL,9,Fshows how important the UK sees "our
OL,10,Frelationship with the Trump
OL,11,Fadministration" with the former trade
OL,12,Fsecretary having "unrivalled political
OL,13,Fexperience".
