OL,7,FThe President-elect has threatened to
OL,8,Fintroduce tariffs on the first day of
OL,9,Fhis new government on January 20.
OL,11,FOn Thursday, when faced with questions
OL,12,Fabout the UK's approach to the
OL,13,Fincoming Trump administration, Starmer
OL,14,Fsaid that the UK would "have to make
OL,15,Fsure that we avoid tariffs".
